Using the full power of wifi technology, you can check if there are hidden cameras and if your ISP provides the speed you pay for, detect your dns server. App find, ping and identifies all devices connected to your network, analyzes download speed as well as connection delays, displaying detailed network information in real time on the screen of your mobile device. Also you can use app with proxy connection or work with vpn enabled.
